<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %> | Business Incubator</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100..900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow">
        
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 pb-16 pt-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold text-black mb-6 tracking-tighter">
                WE BUILD <br>
                <span class="bg-[#FFDE59] px-4 border-4 border-black shadow-neo inline-block transform -rotate-2">FUTURE</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-800 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-bold border-2 border-black p-4 bg-white shadow-neo-sm mt-8">
                // Not just an incubator. We are a factory of dreams, built with hard code and bold ideas.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-20">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="bg-[#FF90E8] border-4 border-black p-10 shadow-neo rounded-none transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-black text-white border-4 border-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6">
                        🚀
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4 uppercase">The Vision</h2>
                    <p class="font-bold text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-black pl-4">
                        To create a chaotic yet organized space where developers turn coffee into scalable businesses. We don't believe in limits.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#5465FF] text-white border-4 border-black p-10 shadow-neo rounded-none transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white text-black border-4 border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6">
                        🎯
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4 uppercase">The Mission</h2>
                    <p class="font-bold text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-white pl-4">
                        Empowering 1000+ startups with "Neo-Brutal" tools. No corporate fluff, just straight-up value and solid backend logic.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-black text-[#FFDE59] py-4 border-y-4 border-black mb-20 marquee-container rotate-1">
            <div class="marquee-content text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
                Code • Create • Sleep (Optional) • Deploy • Scale • Cash Out • Repeat • No Bugs Just Features • 
                Code • Create • Sleep (Optional) • Deploy • Scale • Cash Out • Repeat • No Bugs Just Features •
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-24 max-w-4xl">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-black text-center mb-16 underline decoration-[#FFDE59] decoration-8 underline-offset-8">HOW IT STARTED</h2>
            
            <div class="relative border-l-8 border-black ml-4 md:ml-1/2 md:pl-0 space-y-12">
                
                <div class="relative md:flex items-center justify-between group">
                    <div class="absolute -left-3 md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 w-6 h-6 bg-black border-4 border-white rounded-full z-10"></div>
                    <div class="ml-10 md:ml-0 md:w-[45%] md:pr-8 md:text-right">
                        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 shadow-neo-sm">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-[#FFDE59] inline-block px-2 border-2 border-black mb-2">2024</h3>
                            <p class="font-medium">The idea was born in a garage (literally). We had one server and zero money.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block md:w-[45%]"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative md:flex items-center justify-between group">
                    <div class="absolute -left-3 md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 w-6 h-6 bg-black border-4 border-white rounded-full z-10"></div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block md:w-[45%]"></div>
                    <div class="ml-10 md:ml-0 md:w-[45%] md:pl-8">
                        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 shadow-neo-sm">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-[#FF90E8] inline-block px-2 border-2 border-black mb-2">2025</h3>
                            <p class="font-medium">First 10 startups joined. We crashed the database twice. It was glorious.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative md:flex items-center justify-between group">
                    <div class="absolute -left-3 md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 w-6 h-6 bg-black border-4 border-white rounded-full z-10"></div>
                    <div class="ml-10 md:ml-0 md:w-[45%] md:pr-8 md:text-right">
                        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 shadow-neo-sm">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-[#5465FF] text-white inline-block px-2 border-2 border-black mb-2">2026</h3>
                            <p class="font-medium">We are here now. Global domination mode activated. 🚀</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block md:w-[45%]"></div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#00F0FF] border-y-4 border-black py-16 mb-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
                 <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10 text-center border-4 border-black bg-white inline-block px-6 py-2 shadow-neo mx-auto block w-fit">THE NUMBERS</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-8 text-center">
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-6xl font-black mb-2">50+</h4>
                        <p class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Startups</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-6xl font-black mb-2">200+</h4>
                        <p class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Mentors</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-6xl font-black mb-2">∞</h4>
                        <p class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Coffees</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-24 max-w-6xl">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-black text-center mb-12">THE MANIFESTO</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="border-4 border-black p-6 bg-[#FAFAFA] hover:bg-[#FFDE59] transition-colors duration-300">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-code text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Code First</h3>
                    <p>Talk is cheap. Show us the repo. We value builders over talkers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-4 border-black p-6 bg-[#FAFAFA] hover:bg-[#FF90E8] transition-colors duration-300">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Move Fast</h3>
                    <p>Break things if you have to. Just don't break production on Friday.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-4 border-black p-6 bg-[#FAFAFA] hover:bg-[#5465FF] hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-users text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Community</h3>
                    <p>A lone wolf dies, but the pack survives. We help each other.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-black text-white p-12 md:p-20 text-center border-4 border-[#FFDE59] shadow-neo relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">READY TO BREAK THE RULES?</h2>
                    <p class="text-xl mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-300">Join the incubator that actually cares about your code, not just your pitch deck.</p>
                    <a href="<%= routes.signupRoute %>" class="inline-block bg-[#FFDE59] text-black text-2xl font-bold px-10 py-4 border-4 border-white shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#fff] hover:translate-y-1 hover:shadow-none transition-all">
                        START BUILDING NOW
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#FF90E8] rounded-full opacity-20 -translate-x-10 -translate-y-10"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-48 h-48 bg-[#5465FF] rounded-full opacity-20 translate-x-10 translate-y-10"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>